    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own. This car is in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who needs a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of her, and she\u2019s ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today! If you\u2019re looking for a smooth, worry-free drive at a fair price, come take a look. I'd love to chat and show you around!",
