    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2007 Porsche 911 Carrera S featuring the 3.8L M97.01 flat-six powerplant. This unit delivers linear power delivery with a crisp 7,200 RPM redline, paired with a precise G97 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing adaptive damping that remains composed under high lateral G-loads. Recent service includes a preventive water pump replacement and a clutch slave cylinder refresh to maintain hydraulic integrity. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road-rash consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including bore-scope inspection results and oil chemistry\u2014remain within optimal parameters. The interior features the Sport Chrono package, offering sharper throttle mapping and increased PSM intervention thresholds. A true enthusiast's specimen that balances analog feedback with modern reliability.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
