    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera presented in classic Basalt Black Metallic over a Black leather interior. This vehicle represents a solid, honest example of the 991.1 generation, perfect for an enthusiast who values mechanical integrity and a documented history. The exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like shine; however, in the interest of full transparency, there are minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger fender consistent with regular road use. The 19-inch Carrera wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with approximately 60% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a focused environment. The leather seats show light softening and minor bolster wear on the driver\u2019s side, but remain free of rips or fading. All electronics, including the PCM navigation system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this Porsche shines. It has been serviced exclusively by authorized dealers and reputable specialists, with a folder of receipts included in the sale. The most recent service included an oil change, brake fluid flush, and a multi-point inspection that confirmed no active leaks or immediate needs. The PDK transmission shifts crisply, and the naturally aspirated flat-six provides a linear, soulful power delivery. This is not a garage queen, but a reliable, high-performing sports car that has been driven and maintained with an open checkbook. I welcome pre-purchase inspections at the buyer's expense.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
